name: YouCanDoIt?
description:
Help the chicken climb many obstacles to meet friends
Your finger abilities help you clear the game.

Move the chicken to the target

  • Try to clear the game

  • How to play is simple. You can move the chicken to the target point.

  • Drag with the mouse to jump the chicken.

  • Sometimes you can get angry while playing this game.

  • Feel the annoyance starting from scratch

  • The genre of this game is casual.
